Comments: Note: The MYCN rearrangement is a deletion of exons 2 - 3. One of the breakpoints is within exon 2. Functional significance is undetermined.
Note: The MYCN rearrangement is an inversion of exons 2 - 3. One of the breakpoints is within exon 2. Functional significance is undetermined.

Note: The MYCN - NBAS rearrangement is an inversion that results in a fusion of MYCN exons 1 - 3 to NBAS exons 32 - 52. One of the breakpoints is within MYCN exon 3. Functional significance is undetermined.
